    "name": "Grave Seasons",
    "steam_appid": 3255110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在经历了一场惊心动魄的越狱后，你终于抵达了新的家园——灰岭镇。但是，这座诗歌般美好的田园小镇，却弥漫着令人不安的氛围。在你努力开展崭新的农耕生活，并试图融入社区的同时，小镇却开始发生谋杀案，刚刚起步的平静生活又变得危机四伏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《送葬季》是一款以叙事为主导的农场模拟经营游戏，但温馨景色只是表象，背后暗藏着恐怖反转——小镇中潜伏着超自然连环杀手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/b2e13cedf1b3296b417097fe5d7e35eb.avif?t=1772477105\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras_big/b2e13cedf1b3296b417097fe5d7e35eb.avif?t=1772477105 width=1170 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/4e0d1f16b73913fa2d57fced246e4aac.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/4e0d1f16b73913fa2d57fced246e4aac.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/45b83dc00b5c7939b7aca106567d2bbe.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/45b83dc00b5c7939b7aca106567d2bbe.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/45b83dc00b5c7939b7aca106567d2bbe.mp4?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>农场经营危机重重</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植作物、钓鱼、采矿，并通过在镇上出售商品参与当地经济的运转。但请记住，你所收获的东西都将在揭开灰岭镇的谜团中发挥着举足轻重的作用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/6be7238f32a9106e42fc03eddfd20ecc.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/6be7238f32a9106e42fc03eddfd20ecc.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/8729b5482d58c28ddd7d791ff2047630.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/8729b5482d58c28ddd7d791ff2047630.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/8729b5482d58c28ddd7d791ff2047630.mp4?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逐步揭开凶案面纱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造化弄人，你被卷入了这座温馨小镇中突如其来的命案中。寻找线索并调查个性各异的镇民，并揭露背后的黑暗真相。反正大家都是朋友，偶尔的“窥探隐私”应该也是无可厚非的吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/42eb2201c0a4ad8252e00eaf97c9d555.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/42eb2201c0a4ad8252e00eaf97c9d555.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/6c10a7ab027ec47497c5b174ee0cd910.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/6c10a7ab027ec47497c5b174ee0cd910.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/6c10a7ab027ec47497c5b174ee0cd910.mp4?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保护下一个受害者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找并制作珍贵物品，抵御正在小镇中游荡的威胁。善用你的侦查才能，找出下一个受害者，并遏制悲惨事件的蔓延。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/801a0fb345191515a28977667f916f86.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/801a0fb345191515a28977667f916f86.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/7791d65872c6f77e451750548615f5c7.poster.avif?t=1772477105\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/7791d65872c6f77e451750548615f5c7.webm?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255110/extras/7791d65872c6f77e451750548615f5c7.mp4?t=1772477105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恋爱交友也需谨慎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揪出连环杀手并非易事，为此，你需要完成镇民的任务并赢得他们的信任。你的所作所为或无所作为都将影响故事的发展。而且，如你所想，你甚至可与杀手坠入爱河。</p>",
